{"tid":416353,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"excel sorting 問題","createTime":"2017-09-27T16:48:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-30T03:17:56.000Z","uid":6044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f836a22027c0210c7b85172401d1fe1a737a0434","tid":416353,"uid":6044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T16:48:32.000Z","msg":"有幾百行row data<br />\n有部分data group左入去row<br />\n咁摺疊左方便揾資料<br />\n但一sort佢by value<br />\nData group就亂晒<br />\n可唔可以sort完之後<br />\nData 跟番之前個row group<br />\n唔該先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"263f12b46f9f5529ee9982eca1ceb9456e1c6749","tid":416353,"uid":5499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T16:49:40.000Z","msg":"唔明，有無圖望下"},{"pid":"a86cd319f62eb7de15ded47a4f6f8ebe60599bdb","tid":416353,"uid":6044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T17:03:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔明，有無圖望下</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/28/010305_0c64873d0ad395876be6b264d05a783f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F28%2F010305_0c64873d0ad395876be6b264d05a783f.jpg&h=8d9bca61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nRow2,row3係row1 group<br />\nRow5,row6係row4 group<br />\n平時係摺疊左，要㩒出來先睇到<br />\n咁我sort by date col1<br />\n但一sort row2,row3,row5,row6就會亂左<br />\n唔再係個group入面"},{"pid":"be5d38a25c3139e1d8d94b90248551610f7c279c","tid":416353,"uid":29487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T17:48:41.000Z","msg":"Col1 每行都入返日期咪唔會亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：9up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cdea5e20b74cac59a53b3b8cf433d6a53119de1","tid":416353,"uid":13025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T17:53:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Col1 每行都入返日期咪唔會亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=