 />\n有沒其他方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n客人資料咪入column <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上手整開<br />\n有幾萬條data<br />\n我無理由同佢執<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n究竟有沒得sort by group<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"335ab66b5c5384b2b57409728b4ca8c651134c36","tid":416353,"uid":57633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T06:58:38.000Z","msg":"舊唔整得, 咪整新<br />\n你咁樣好難sort架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba624437e58593ad232eea580fc832fc3eed8b40","tid":416353,"uid":57633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T07:01:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>舊唔整得, 咪整新<br />\n你咁樣好難sort架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nrow 2 3 5 6平時要入返日期<br />\n<br />\nrow 1 4 就唔好再入<br />\n要睇返row 1 4總數咪另外開個sheet用公式計返出黎"},{"pid":"3481a77b325ac6f2aeddd9ad3a36f395cd8109c5","tid":416353,"uid":108540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T07:02:02.000Z","msg":"加個col 做gp_no 每個row 拉返gp幾<br />\nmulitple criteria sort gp_no 再 sort date<br />\n<br />\n唔知有無理解錯"},{"pid":"61b4164d93ac904c4ce27684da211140f3095647","tid":416353,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T03:21:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Col1 每行都入返日期咪唔會亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：9up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有時除左日期仲有客人資料係下一行同一group<br />\n但一sort就亂<br />\n有沒其他方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n客人資料咪入column <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上手整開<br />\n有幾萬條data<br />\n我無理由同佢執<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n究竟有沒得sort by group<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你咁懶 excel唔岩你用"},{"pid":"cedde8b23a5469ec65de711976b166afd2d5740a","tid":416353,"uid":6777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T03:28:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Col1 每行都入返日期咪唔會亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：9up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有時除左日期仲有客人資料係下一行同一group<br />\n但一sort就亂<br />\n有沒其他方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n客人資料咪入column <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上手整開<br />\n有幾萬條data<br />\n我無理由同佢執<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n究竟有沒得sort by group<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你咁懶 excel唔岩你用</blockquote><br />\n開新行，係B1度用function<br />\n=if(countA(A2)=0,A1,A2)"},{"pid":"b85b2710e8b8828702fabf505e9984b8f0d948ab","tid":416353,"uid":6777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T03:40:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Col1 每行都入返日期咪唔會亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：9up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有時除左日期仲有客人資料係下一行同一group<br />\n但一sort就亂<br />\n有沒其他方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n客人資料咪入column <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上手整開<br />\n有幾萬條data<br />\n我無理由同佢執<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n究竟有沒得sort by group<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你咁懶 excel唔岩你用</blockquote><br />\n開新行，係B1度用function<br />\n=if(countA(